---

ğŸš€ 4ï¸âƒ£ Advanced Enhancements (Very Powerful)

You can also add:

{
  "flowchart": {
    "htmlLabels": false,
    "diagramPadding": 20,
    "wrap": true
  }
}

Why?

Option	Benefit

htmlLabels: false	Avoid rendering bugs
diagramPadding	Cleaner margins
wrap: true	Text wraps properly



---

ğŸ’ 5ï¸âƒ£ Role-Based Color Styling (Highly Recommended)

Instead of one color for all nodes, you can define custom classes inside your Mermaid:

Example:

classDef maker fill:#0B3D91,color:#fff,stroke:#062E6F;
classDef system fill:#E8F1FF,color:#000,stroke:#0B3D91;
classDef validation fill:#FFD966,color:#000,stroke:#B8860B;
classDef decision fill:#F8CECC,color:#000,stroke:#B85450;

Then apply:

class Start,S1 maker;
class B2,C2,V3 system;
class BA5,CH6 decision;

ğŸ”¥ This makes:

Maker actions â†’ Blue

System auto-fetch â†’ Light Blue

Validation â†’ Yellow

Decision â†’ Red


Very executive-presentation friendly.


